Abstract = {This paper proposes a new approach for training feed-forward neural
   networks (FNN) by hybrid of cultural algorithm and back-propagation
   algorithm (HCABP). It combines the advantages of the global search
   performed by cultural algorithm over the FNN parameter space and the
   local search of the back-propagation algorithm(BP). Using a function
