   (ATC), Ho Chi Minh City, VIETNAM, OCT 14-16, 2021},
Organization = {IEEE; IEEE Commun Soc; Vietnam Radio Elect Assoc; Ho Chi Minh City Univ
   Technol; Natl Fdn Sci \& Technol Dev},
Abstract = {This paper presents a hybrid technique of combining the BERT embedding
   method and the graph convolutional neural network. This combination is
   then employed to solve the text classification problem. Initially, we
   apply the BERT embedding method to the whole corpus in order to
   transform all the texts into numerical vectors. Then, the graph
   convolutional neural network will be applied to these numerical vectors
   to classify these texts into their appropriate classes. Especially, in
   our approach, we need only a few labeled texts for the model training.
   For the illustration, in this paper, we use the BBC news and the IMDB
   movie reviews datasets to perform our experiments, showing that the
   performance of the graph convolutional neural network model is better
   than the performances of the combination of the BERT embedding method
   with other classical machine learning models.},
